st=Bouloc | first=Pierre | title=Hemp: Industrial Production and Uses | publisher=CABI | year=2013 | isbn=978-1-84593-793-5 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2RX4AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA145 | section=The industrial hemp economy | pp=145-161}} *{{citation |last1=Fike |first1=John |title=Industrial Hemp: Renewed Opportunities for an Ancient Crop |journal=Critical Reviews in Plant Sciences |date=4 January 2017 |volume=35 |issue=5-6 |pages=406–424 |doi=10.1080/07352689.2016.1257842}} ==External links== *{{Commons category inline|Hemp shives}}
