A '''Test CD''' usually refers to a [[compact disc]] containing tracks of [[music]]al and technical [[Audio equipment testing|test]]s and demonstrations. Most of the tracks are made of [[Signal (electrical engineering)|electronic signal]]s and pure [[Frequency|frequencies]]. The purpose of these specialized compact discs is to make accurate tests and calibrate [[audio equipment]].
A wide variety of CD-DA test discs have been produced in the past, and a few are still in production:
* Stereophile Test CD 2<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.stereophile.com/features/338/index.html|title=Stereophile Test CD 2|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * CD-CHECK Test Disc<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digital-recordings.com/cdcheck/cdcheck.html|title=CD-CHECK Test Disc|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * NAB Broadcast & Audio Test CD, Vol 1 (still in production) * NAB Broadcast & Audio Test CD, Vol 2 (still in production) * Precision Test Signals * The Ultimate Test CD * CBS Records CD-1 Standard Test Disc<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cieri.net/Documenti/Misure audio/Test Discs/CD Test Disc - CBS Records Professional Series - CD-1 Standard Test Disc for measuring CD player performance with E.I.A. standard signals.pdf|title=CBS Records CD-1 Standard Test Disc|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> (with EIA standard signals) * EIAJ CD-1 Standard Test Disc (YGDS 13) (EIAJ Standard CP-308) * Denon Audio Technical CD 38C39-7147<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cieri.net/Documenti/Misure audio/Test Discs/CD Test Disc - Denon - Audio Technical CD - 38C39-7147 (1984).pdf|title=Denon Audio Technical CD|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * Japan Audio Society Audio Test CD-1 (YDDS-2)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cieri.net/Documenti/Misure audio/Test Discs/CD Test Disc - Japan Audio Society - Audio Test CD-1 - 91 Test Signals for Home and Laboratory Use - YDDS-2 (1984).pdf|title=Japan Audio Society Audio Test CD-1|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * Philips Test Sample 4a<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cieri.net/Documenti/Misure audio/Test Discs/CD Test Disc - Philips - Test Sample 4a - 410 056-2 (1982).pdf|title=Philips Test Sample 4a|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> * Sony Test CD Type 3 YEDS-7 * Technics CD Test Disc SH-CD001
